name: GotoDaily
tag_list: social-network, coupons, shopping, coupon-codes, promo-codes, savings, discounts, bargains, sales
overview:
GotoDaily is a social shopping community. GotoDaily.com makes it easy to discover, share and recommend online store coupons, deals, and promotions. GotoDaily offers great collection of money-saving coupons for many products and services, including women’s fashion, clothing, toys, gifts, flowers, pizza, dry cleaners, digital cameras, and more. Perhaps the key offering from GotoDaily is its social networking platform, which enables members to create online profiles, create albums, upload photos, send and receive messages, create wish lists, subscribe to their favorite stores, connect with friends, and more.

With GotoDaily, it’s easy to share coupons and deals with friends and the community. Members can rate and review their favorite (and not-so-favorite) stores, while discovering great online stores they never knew existed. Gotodaily aims to help people save money whenever they shop online.
